00:43:00,980 --> 00:43:02,730
Thanks. You're back early.

459
00:43:02,730 --> 00:43:04,690
- Sorry for the wait.
- Not at all.

460
00:43:06,570 --> 00:43:08,280
Shall we go in?

461
00:43:08,280 --> 00:43:09,850
We're almost home.

462
00:43:09,850 --> 00:43:12,360
My little koala, let's go home.

463
00:43:14,490 --> 00:43:16,840
Let's go home.

464
00:43:16,840 --> 00:43:18,520
Let me open the door for you.

465
00:43:18,520 --> 00:43:20,180
- Thanks.
- Here we go.

466
00:43:24,020 --> 00:43:27,790
We're home.

467
00:43:30,360 --> 00:43:35,790
<i>Everything became clear to me when I saw Satoko with Ogata.</i>

468
00:43:36,680 --> 00:43:43,270
Satoko wanted to kill her husband, so she could be with Ogata.

469
00:43:44,350 --> 00:43:50,750
That's why she threatened Maho and demanded to kill him.

470
00:43:52,810 --> 00:43:56,800
So were they in love with each other the whole time?

471
00:43:59,540 --> 00:44:01,960
And it has led...

472
00:44:02,720 --> 00:44:05,720
to another tragedy.

473
00:44:06,450 --> 00:44:08,650
Tragedy?

474
00:44:16,180 --> 00:44:18,190
Actually...

475
00:44:25,460 --> 00:44:27,170
Excuse me.

476
00:44:32,930 --> 00:44:34,840
Hello?

477
00:44:34,840 --> 00:44:38,420
It's about Yuri Totsuka that you'd inquired about the other day.

478
00:44:38,420 --> 00:44:40,130
Yes.

479
00:44:40,130 --> 00:44:42,470
<i>She passed away.</i>

480
00:44:42,470 --> 00:44:44,000
What?

481
00:44:44,000 --> 00:44:48,170
Yuri Totsuka is dead.

482
00:44:49,960 --> 00:44:52,320
She died?

