00:45:07,540 --> 00:45:09,470
<i>Everything was going to be all right.</i>

486
00:45:09,470 --> 00:45:12,910
<i>I tried to believe the world that I lived in wasn't a living hell.</i>

487
00:45:12,910 --> 00:45:15,330
<i>Has someone else died?</i>

